back to intuition,

00:01:25.740 --> 00:01:28.517 align:middle line:10%
coming back to listening to our
patients in a very deep way.

00:01:28.517 --> 00:01:30.600 align:middle line:84%
And I think this is what
patients are looking for.

00:01:30.600 --> 00:01:32.920 align:middle line:84%
They're very tired of
being talked down to,

00:01:32.920 --> 00:01:34.770 align:middle line:84%
