>> Yes.

00:16:27.290 --> 00:16:29.720 align:middle line:84%
That's step four is
asking for inner guidance.

00:16:29.720 --> 00:16:31.760 align:middle line:84%
And as a way of asking
for inner guidance,

00:16:31.760 --> 00:16:33.920 align:middle line:84%
I teach a technique known
as remote viewing, which

00:16:33.920 --> 00:16:37.280 align:middle line:84%
is a form of intuitively tuning
into a person at a distance

00:16:37.280 --> 00:16:39.510 align:middle line:84%
or tuning into your
body or tuning into--

00:16:39.510 --> 00:16:41.360 align:middle line:84%
>> I mean, people are
doing experiments even

00:16:41.360 --> 00:16:42.985 align:middle line:84%
in the government on
this, aren't they?

00:16:42.985 --> 00:16:45.500 align:middle line:84%
>> Oh, for 20 years they
did top secret experiments

00:16:45.500 --> 00:16:48.410 align:middle line:84%
at the Stanford Research
Institute on remote viewing.

00:16:48.410 --> 00:16:50.690 align:middle line:84%
And they mainly used it
for military purposes,

00:16:50.690 --> 00:16:53.540 align:middle line:84%
where they would have remote
viewers in Stanford tuning

00:16:53.540 --> 00:16:56.450 align:middle line:84%
into what was going on in
Russia during the Cold War,

00:16:56.450 --> 00:16:59.750 align:middle line:84%
and they were trying to use
it for a strategic military

00:16:59.750 --> 00:17:01.460 align:middle line:90%
espionage, basically.

00:17:01.460 --> 00:17:03.800 align:middle line:84%
And then the top
secret ban was lifted

00:17:03.800 --> 00:17:06.140 align:middle line:84%
and all the scientists
started talking about it.

00:17:06.140 --> 00:17:08.670 align:middle line:84%
And I don't use remote
viewing for those purposes.

00:17:08.670 --> 00:17:10.310 align:middle line:84%
I use remote
viewing for healing.

00:17:10.310 --> 00:17:13.097 align:middle line:84%
And I teach every one of my
patients how to tune in to,

00:17:13.097 --> 00:17:14.930 align:middle line:84%
let's say if they're
about to go into a job,

00:17:14.930 --> 00:17:16.483 align:middle line:84%
to tune into their
boss to find out

00:17:16.483 --> 00:17:18.650 align:middle line:84%
if this is the type of
person you want to work with.

00:17:18.650 --> 00:17:20.150 align:middle line:84%
And they get all
kinds of intuitions

00:17:20.150 --> 00:17:21.680 align:middle line:90%
before you even go in.

00:17:21.680 --> 00:17:24.440 align:middle line:84%
And to make decisions that
factor in your remote viewing

00:17:24.440 --> 00:17:25.240 align:middle line:90%
experience.

00:17:25.240 --> 00:17:25.390 align:middle line:90%
>> All right.

00:17:25.390 --> 00:17:26.990 align:middle line:90%
Let's do a little bit of this.

00:17:26.990 --> 00:17:28.060 align:middle line:90%
How do you do it?

00:17:28.060 --> 00:17:31.730 align:middle line:84%
Say somebody has
a friend who they

00:17:31.730 --> 00:17:33.860 align:middle line:84%
haven't heard from
in a long time,

00:17:33.860 --> 00:17:35.230 align:middle line:90%
and the friend has been ill.

00:17:35.230 --> 00:17:35.650 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:17:35.650 --> 00:17:36.508 align:middle line:90%
Yes, yes.

00:17:36.508 --> 00:17:39.050 align:middle line:84%
>> Now you sit down, you want
to find out how this person is.

00:17:39.050 --> 00:17:39.950 align:middle line:90%
How do you do that?

00:17:39.950 --> 00:17:40.480 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:17:40.480 --> 00:17:42.470 align:middle line:84%
Well, what you do is
you just get very quiet

00:17:42.470 --> 00:17:45.285 align:middle line:84%
and you begin to breathe, and
whatever thoughts you have,

00:17:45.285 --> 00:17:47.660 align:middle line:84%
all of the laundry list of
things to do and the problems,

00:17:47.660 --> 00:17:49.830 align:middle line:84%
you can set those aside
just for a few moments.

00:17:49.830 --> 00:17:51.380 align:middle line:84%
They'll be there
when you come back.

00:17:51.380 --> 00:17:53.810 align:middle line:84%
And to go in and
just use the breath

00:17:53.810 --> 00:17:57.710 align:middle line:84%
as a hypnotic incantation to
center the self on the breath.

00:17:57.710 --> 00:17:59.720 align:middle line:84%
If you just breathe and
breathe and breathe,

00:17:59.720 --> 00:18:01.220 align:middle line:84%
that helps you get
out of your mind.

00:18:01.220 --> 00:18:04.310 align:middle line:84%
Then you sit in that quiet
state and then you very lightly

00:18:04.310 --> 00:18:05.330 align:middle line:90%
tune into your friend.

00:18:05.330 --> 00:18:07.670 align:middle line:84%
You don't try and
visualize anything.

00:18:07.670 --> 00:18:10.570 align:middle line:84%
You just ask for any images
or impressions or knowings

00:18:10.570 --> 00:18:13.533 align:middle line:84%
that come, and then you just
wait and see what you get.

00:18:13.533 --> 00:18:15.950 align:middle line:84%
And you might get a sense, I
need to call this friend now.

00:18:15.950 --> 00:18:16.908 align:middle line:90%
This friend is in need.

00:18:16.908 --> 00:18:18.330 align:middle line:90%
I need to do something.

00:18:18.330 --> 00:18:19.850 align:middle line:84%
And then you'll
pick up the phone.

00:18:19.850 --> 00:18:22.603 align:middle line:84%
Or you might get a sense this
person is feeling a lot better.

00:18:22.603 --> 00:18:24.020 align:middle line:84%
They're getting
their energy back.

00:18:24.020 --> 00:18:25.850 align:middle line:84%
You'll have the sense
in your own body

00:18:25.850 --> 00:18:28.170 align:middle line:84%
or through images
what's going on

00:18:28.170 --> 00:18:30.650 align:middle line:84%
and you can get all
kinds of knowledge

00:18:30.650 --> 00:18:31.850 align:middle line:90%
about how to help people.

00:18:31.850 --> 00:18:33.560 align:middle line:90%
That's how I use my intuition--

00:18:33.560 --> 00:18:35.440 align:middle line:90%
only it's for love and service.

00:18:35.440 --> 00:18:37.940 align:middle line:84%
I don't if you put me in a place
to predict lottery numbers,

00:18:37.940 --> 00:18:39.740 align:middle line:84%
I could never do that,
because I'm not good at it,

00:18:39.740 --> 00:18:41.390 align:middle line:84%
nor do I have any
interest in it.

00:18:41.390 --> 00:18:44.330 align:middle line:84%
But if you put me in a situation
where I can help somebody,

00:18:44.330 --> 00:18:47.140 align:middle line:84%
then my intuition really
becomes amplified.

00:18:47.140 --> 00:18:49.160 align:middle line:84%
And I think that's true
for a lot of people.

00:18:49.160 --> 00:18:50.690 align:middle line:84%
When it's used for
heart purposes,

00:18:50.690 --> 00:18:52.310 align:middle line:84%
if you want to tune
into your friend,

00:18:52.310 --> 00:18:53.360 align:middle line:84%
you're not sure
how they're doing,

00:18:53.360 --> 00:18:54.837 align:middle line:84%
you want to help
them in some way,

00:18:54.837 --> 00:18:56.420 align:middle line:84%
then the intuition
really gets turned.

00:18:56.420 --> 00:18:58.580 align:middle line:84%
And remote viewing
can help with that.

00:18:58.580 --> 00:19:00.680 align:middle line:84%
>> Let's talk about it
in a different context.

00:19:00.680 --> 00:19:02.640 align:middle line:90%
Let's talk about it in business.

00:19:02.640 --> 00:19:04.090 align:middle line:90%
What about if you're a salesman?

00:19:04.090 --> 00:19:05.030 align:middle line:90%
>> Mhm.

00:19:05.030 --> 00:19:05.690 align:middle line:90%
Mhm.

00:19:05.690 --> 00:19:05.780 align:middle line:90%
Oh, you--

00:19:05.780 --> 00:19:08.420 align:middle line:84%
>> Can you do this to find out
whether this is a good time

00:19:08.420 --> 00:19:10.640 align:middle line:90%
to make a pitch on a sale?

00:19:10.640 --> 00:19:11.960 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, absolutely.

00:19:11.960 --> 00:19:13.670 align:middle line:84%
Remote viewing and
intuitive readings

00:19:13.670 --> 00:19:15.223 align:middle line:90%
give you a sense of timing.

00:19:15.223 --> 00:19:17.390 align:middle line:84%
You get a sense of the
timing is right for something

00:19:17.390 --> 00:19:20.270 align:middle line:84%
and when to jump on it, or
if the timing is not right.

00:19:20.270 --> 00:19:22.160 align:middle line:84%
What I was alluding
to about tuning

00:19:22.160 --> 00:19:24.707 align:middle line:84%
into an intuitive yes or
no, you tune in you say,

00:19:24.707 --> 00:19:26.540 align:middle line:84%
is this a good time to
promote this product?

00:19:26.540 --> 00:19:29.090 align:middle line:84%
You go in, you ask for
intuitive yes or no.

00:19:29.090 --> 00:19:30.560 align:middle line:84%
Do you get a
quickening of energy,

00:19:30.560 --> 00:19:32.923 align:middle line:84%
do you get a sense of
excitement pulling you forward,

00:19:32.923 --> 00:19:35.090 align:middle line:84%
or do you get a sinking
feeling or that nothing much

00:19:35.090 --> 00:19:36.890 align:middle line:84%
is happening, you're
trying to effort?

00:19:36.890 --> 00:19:38.840 align:middle line:84%
You need to factor
in those intuitions.

00:19:38.840 --> 00:19:40.970 align:middle line:84%
And if you get a
no, then you wait.

00:19:40.970 --> 00:19:42.080 align:middle line:90%
There's wisdom in waiting.

00:19:42.080 --> 00:19:42.590 align:middle line:90%
We don't know--

00:19:42.590 --> 00:19:43.910 align:middle line:90%
>> Suppose you get nothing?

00:19:43.910 --> 00:19:45.165 align:middle line:90%
>> Then you don't act.

00:19:45.165 --> 00:19:46.540 align:middle line:84%
You wait until
you get something.

00:19:46.540 --> 00:19:47.630 align:middle line:90%
>> Do you trust this?

00:19:47.630 --> 00:19:49.040 align:middle line:90%
>> Implicitly.

00:19:49.040 --> 00:19:52.623 align:middle line:84%
I have learned to really craft
my whole life around this,

00:19:52.623 --> 00:19:53.540 align:middle line:90%
because I've learned--

00:19:53.540 --> 00:19:55.670 align:middle line:84%
I've not listened
for so long and I

00:19:55.670 --> 00:19:58.070 align:middle line:84%
saw all of the negative
effects that can happen.

00:19:58.070 --> 00:20:00.290 align:middle line:84%
It was a battering that
happens when people don't

00:20:00.290 --> 00:20:01.850 align:middle line:90%
listen to their intuition.

00:20:01.850 --> 00:20:05.793 align:middle line:84%
And for those who do, life
expands and becomes incredible.

00:20:05.793 --> 00:20:07.460 align:middle line:84%
When people get into
the intuitive flow,

00:20:07.460 --> 00:20:09.020 align:middle line:90%
synchronicities happen.

00:20:09.020 --> 00:20:11.300 align:middle line:84%
Magic happens that
could never go on

00:20:11.300 --> 00:20:12.890 align:middle line:90%
with just the rational mind.

00:20:12.890 --> 00:20:15.750 align:middle line:84%
The rational mind is wonderful,
but it can't understand things

00:20:15.750 --> 00:20:16.550 align:middle line:90%
like love.

00:20:16.550 --> 00:20:19.580 align:middle line:84%
It can't understand things like
the mystery of illness or death

00:20:19.580 --> 00:20:20.630 align:middle line:90%
or intuition.

00:20:20.630 --> 00:20:22.470 align:middle line:84%
It just doesn't
have that capacity.

00:20:22.470 --> 00:20:24.650 align:middle line:84%
But when you begin to get
into the intuitive flow,

00:20:24.650 --> 00:20:26.450 align:middle line:84%
it's like you get in
touch with a pulse.

00:20:26.450 --> 00:20:29.450 align:middle line:84%
Then you start meeting people
and pass cross and deja

00:20:29.450 --> 00:20:32.000 align:middle line:84%
vus happen, and all these
intuitive experiences

00:20:32.000 --> 00:20:34.130 align:middle line:84%
become part of
everyday life, which

00:20:34.130 --> 00:20:35.820 align:middle line:90%
brings magic and wonder to it.

00:20:35.820 --> 00:20:38.150 align:middle line:84%
And plus, it's a lot easier
to navigate this world

00:20:38.150 --> 00:20:40.170 align:middle line:84%
when you're in touch
with this flow.

00:20:40.170 --> 00:20:42.420 align:middle line:84%
>> Suppose you're
very intuitive,

00:20:42.420 --> 00:20:45.140 align:middle line:84%
and you really get a fix
and you know something.

00:20:45.140 --> 00:20:45.940 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:20:45.940 --> 00:20:46.773 align:middle line:90%
>> You just know it.

00:20:46.773 --> 00:20:47.573 align:middle line:90%
>> Right.

00:20:47.573 --> 00:20:48.420 align:middle line:90%
Right.

00:20:48.420 --> 00:20:50.080 align:middle line:90%
>> And it doesn't happen.

00:20:50.080 --> 00:20:52.560 align:middle line:84%
How do you keep the faith
when it doesn't happen,

00:20:52.560 --> 00:20:54.900 align:middle line:90%
when you're so sure?

00:20:54.900 --> 00:20:57.300 align:middle line:10%
>> Well, I would question
then the sense of timing.

00:20:57.300 --> 00:20:58.728 align:middle line:10%
Because sometimes
you can tune in

00:20:58.728 --> 00:21:00.520 align:middle line:10%
and know that something
is going to happen,

00:21:00.520 --> 00:21:02.347 align:middle line:10%
and yet, it's not
in your time frame.

00:21:02.347 --> 00:21:03.930 align:middle line:84%
And so what I suggest
at those points,

00:21:03.930 --> 00:21:07.050 align:middle line:84%
particularly when people have
premonitory dreams, to write it

00:21:07.050 --> 00:21:09.060 align:middle line:90%
down and then just wait.

00:21:09.060 --> 00:21:12.180 align:middle line:84%
The difficulty with intuition
is there's no time and no space,

00:21:12.180 --> 00:21:14.430 align:middle line:84%
and so it's harder
to pinpoint timing.

00:21:14.430 --> 00:21:16.710 align:middle line:84%
I had psychic
dreams that happened

00:21:16.710 --> 00:21:20.100 align:middle line:84%
10 years before the
actual event happened.

00:21:20.100 --> 00:21:22.917 align:middle line:84%
And so what I do, I just
chronicle everything

00:21:22.917 --> 00:21:24.000 align:middle line:90%
and I remember everything.

00:21:24.000 --> 00:21:26.295 align:middle line:84%
And when something
happens, let's say 10 years

00:21:26.295 --> 00:21:28.170 align:middle line:84%
down the line, I go back
to my dream journal.

00:21:28.170 --> 00:21:30.060 align:middle line:84%
I start and I go
yes this did happen.

00:21:30.060 --> 00:21:33.062 align:middle line:84%
Because it's important to get
feedback on your intuitions

00:21:33.062 --> 00:21:35.520 align:middle line:84%
and see, yes, I dreamed that
this happened and it happened.

00:21:35.520 --> 00:21:36.450 align:middle line:90%
Isn't this exciting?

00:21:36.450 --> 00:21:39.160 align:middle line:84%
And it's a wonderful way of
getting positive feedback.

00:21:39.160 --> 00:21:40.270 align:middle line:90%
>> So be patient.

00:21:40.270 --> 00:21:41.070 align:middle line:90%
Oh you must.

00:21:41.070 --> 00:21:42.300 align:middle line:90%
You can't force anything.

00:21:42.300 --> 00:21:45.570 align:middle line:84%
>> So we sometimes pick things
up that are way in advance--

00:21:45.570 --> 00:21:46.500 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh, that's true.

00:21:46.500 --> 00:21:47.580 align:middle line:90%
That's very true.

00:21:47.580 --> 00:21:49.410 align:middle line:84%
>> --of what is
actually happening now.

00:21:49.410 --> 00:21:49.620 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:21:49.620 --> 00:21:52.080 align:middle line:84%
I had an example of a woman
who came to me recently

00:21:52.080 --> 00:21:55.432 align:middle line:84%
at a workshop and she said, I
got the name of my soulmate,

00:21:55.432 --> 00:21:57.390 align:middle line:84%
I got the date I was
going to meet my soulmate,

00:21:57.390 --> 00:21:59.520 align:middle line:90%
it was 10 years to that day.

00:21:59.520 --> 00:22:02.598 align:middle line:84%
And she met him and she
felt that when she met him

00:22:02.598 --> 00:22:04.390 align:middle line:84%
it was amazing because
she didn't like him.

00:22:04.390 --> 00:22:06.230 align:middle line:84%
He was a chauvinist and
she didn't relate to him.

00:22:06.230 --> 00:22:07.772 align:middle line:84%
And she said, but
is there a destiny?

00:22:07.772 --> 00:22:08.910 align:middle line:90%
Do I need to marry him?

00:22:08.910 --> 00:22:10.417 align:middle line:90%
And I go, absolutely not.

00:22:10.417 --> 00:22:12.000 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes you pick
things up you don't

00:22:12.000 --> 00:22:13.200 align:middle line:90%
know why you pick things up.

00:22:13.200 --> 00:22:15.310 align:middle line:84%
It's a spiritual
lesson of some sort.

00:22:15.310 --> 00:22:16.807 align:middle line:84%
Things aren't
always as they seem.

00:22:16.807 --> 00:22:19.140 align:middle line:84%
But what people need to do
and what I advised her is you

00:22:19.140 --> 00:22:20.430 align:middle line:90%
must listen to your inner voice.

00:22:20.430 --> 00:22:21.540 align:middle line:90%
Is this your soulmate now?

00:22:21.540 --> 00:22:22.620 align:middle line:90%
Do you want to marry him?

00:22:22.620 --> 00:22:25.320 align:middle line:84%
It was the name of the person,
it was the date of the person,

00:22:25.320 --> 00:22:26.250 align:middle line:90%
but how do you know?

00:22:26.250 --> 00:22:29.890 align:middle line:84%
You have to trust what's
inside more than anything else.

00:22:29.890 --> 00:22:32.470 align:middle line:84%
>> So even if you pick it
up, you don't have to do it.

00:22:32.470 --> 00:22:33.270 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh no.

00:22:33.270 --> 00:22:35.670 align:middle line:84%
You always have to tune in
and say, is this appropriate?

00:22:35.670 --> 00:22:38.010 align:middle line:90%
Is this right?

00:22:38.010 --> 00:22:42.030 align:middle line:84%
>> So are you picking
up probabilities then,

00:22:42.030 --> 00:22:43.530 align:middle line:90%
rather than--

00:22:43.530 --> 00:22:45.900 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I think probability
is a big part of it is that

00:22:45.900 --> 00:22:46.860 align:middle line:90%
